charges.charge_description: 21:841(a)(1) and 841(b)(1)(C) POSSESSION OF COCAINE WITH INTENT TO DISTRIBUTE (1)

charges.charge_disposition: Deft. is committed to the custody of the US BOP for imprisonment for 24 months. Deft. to serve 5 years supervised release. Deft. to pay $50.00 spec. assmnt. (1)

charges.charge_description: On or about July 30, 1993, in Hennepin County, State and District of Minnesota, dft did knowingly, intentionally, and unlawfully possess with intent to distribute approximately 22.9 grams of cocaine and 8.2 grams of cocaine base, also known as crack, in violation of 21 USC 841(a)(1) [4:95-m-162]
